                            <comment id="14455711" author="stevel" created="Thu, 28 Mar 2013 08:19:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attached pom file in question. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14455906" author="stevel" created="Thu, 28 Mar 2013 08:20:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;the includes section is in there, just cut and pasted from elsewhere -and containing unresolvable references &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;          &amp;lt;includes&amp;gt;
            &amp;lt;include&amp;gt;**/Test*.java&amp;lt;/include&amp;gt;
          &amp;lt;/includes&amp;gt;
          &amp;lt;excludes&amp;gt;
            &amp;lt;exclude&amp;gt;**/${test.exclude}.java&amp;lt;/exclude&amp;gt;
            &amp;lt;exclude&amp;gt;${test.exclude.pattern}&amp;lt;/exclude&amp;gt;
            &amp;lt;exclude&amp;gt;**/Test*$*.java&amp;lt;/exclude&amp;gt;
          &amp;lt;/excludes&amp;gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
